<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Bulking Diet Plan</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Light Gray */
    }
    header {
      background-color: #333;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 36px;
    }
    .container {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-around;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .section {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }
    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .food-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; /* Center the image */
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .food-item img {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-top-left-radius: 10px;
      border-top-right-radius: 10px;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; /* Centered image with rounded corners */
      border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
    }
    .food-info {
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
    }
    .food-info strong {
      font-size: 25px;
      color: #333;
      margin-left: 170px;
    }
    .food-info p {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #555;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .macros {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .macro-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Bulking Diet Plan</h1>
</header>



<div class="container">
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Veg</h2>
    <ul>
      <li class="food-item">
        <img src="https://www.onehappyhousewife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/instant-pot-quinoa-20-20211203-600x600.jpg" alt="Quinoa">
        <div class="food-info">
          <strong>Quinoa</strong>
          <p>Quinoa is a complete protein, providing all nine essential amino acids. It is also high in fiber and various nutrients like magnesium, iron, and zinc.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="food-item">
        <img src="https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2022/07/Broccoli-78ec54e.jpg?quality=90&resize=556,505" alt="Broccoli">
        <div class="food-info">
          <strong>Broccoli</strong>
          <p>Broccoli is rich in vitamins C, K, and folate. It also provides fiber and antioxidants, supporting overall health.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="food-item">
        <img src="https://c.ndtvimg.com/2023-10/i3o3r9pg_sweet-potatoes_625x300_23_October_23.jpg?im=FaceCrop,algorithm=dnn,width=1200,height=738" alt="Sweet Potato">
        <div class="food-info">
          <strong>Sweet Potato</strong>
          <p>Sweet potatoes are a great source of complex carbohydrates, fiber, and various vitamins and minerals.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="food-item">
        <img src="https://post.medicalnewstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2021/08/Stocksy_txpa387b205vt9300_Medium_3358820_header-1024x575.jpg" alt="Avocado">
        <div class="food-info">
          <strong>Avocado</strong>
          <p>Avocado is rich in healthy fats, including monounsaturated fat. It also provides vitamins E, C, B6, and folate.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <!-- Add more veg food items here -->
    </ul>
    <div class="macros">
      <h3>Macros (per 100g)</h3>
      <div class="macro-item">
        <span>Quinoa</span>
        <span>Protein: 4g, Carbs: 19g, Fat: 1.6g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-item">
        <span>Broccoli</span>
        <span>Protein: 2.8g, Carbs: 11.2g, Fat: 0.6g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-item">
        <span>Sweet Potato</span>
        <span>Protein: 1.6g, Carbs: 20.7g, Fat: 0.1g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-item">
        <span>Avocado</span>
        <span>Protein: 2g, Carbs: 8.5g, Fat: 14.7g</span>
      </div>
      <!-- Add more macros for veg items here -->
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Non-Veg</h2>
    <ul>
      <li class="food-item">
        <img src="https://www.allrecipes.com/thmb/Z5s08uvHYI2dg5LAd0vwoA47Ngo=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/240208_simplebakedchickenbreasts_mfs_step1_0181-1-4x3-250b3f145a194aa3bab88e94e3cbae73.jpg" alt="Chicken Breast">
        <div class="food-info">
          <strong>Chicken Breast</strong>
          <p>Chicken breast is a lean source of protein, low in fat, and rich in vitamins and minerals such as niacin, vitamin B6, phosphorus, and selenium.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="food-item">
        <img src="https://images.seattletimes.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/11292023_13-salmon-trucking_131034.jpg?d=2040x1361" alt="Salmon">
        <div class="food-info">
          <strong>Salmon</strong>
          <p>Salmon is a fatty fish that provides omega-3 fatty acids, high-quality protein, and a variety of vitamins and minerals.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="food-item">
        <img src="https://www.bhg.com/thmb/Ulaofb5w0p2F-IcOOvxNYx9hWeo=/550x0/filters:no_upscale():strip_icc()/101201681-caf3126916884b93824a294662c14ca5.jpg" alt="Beef Steak">
        <div class="food-info">
          <strong>Beef Steak</strong>
          <p>Beef steak is a rich source of protein, iron, zinc, and several B-vitamins essential for overall health and muscle function.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="food-item">
        <img src="https://media.post.rvohealth.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/tuna-fish-can-1200x628-facebook-1200x628.jpg" alt="Tuna">
        <div class="food-info">
          <strong>Tuna</strong>
          <p>canned tuna is a healthful food rich in protein and contains many vitamins and minerals such as B-Complex vitamins, Vitamins A and D as well as iron, selenium and phosphorus</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <!-- Add more non-veg food items here -->
    </ul>
    <div class="macros">
      <h3>Macros (per 100g)</h3>
      <div class="macro-item">
        <span>Chicken Breast</span>
        <span>Protein: 31g, Carbs: 0g, Fat: 3.6g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-item">
        <span>Salmon</span>
        <span>Protein: 25g, Carbs: 0g, Fat: 10.4g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-item">
        <span>Beef Steak</span>
        <span>Protein: 26g, Carbs: 0g, Fat: 17.2g</span>
      </div>
      <div class="macro-item">
        <span>Eggs</span>
        <span>Protein: 13g, Carbs: 1.1g, Fat: 11g</span>
      </div>
      <!-- Add more macros for non-veg items here -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
